== 廣播 ==
在美國，劇集於[[Syfy|Syfy]]上播放，並於[[Amazon_Prime|Amazon Prime]]上以[[串流|串流]]廣播。在加拿大，劇集在[[SPACE_(電視頻道)|SPACE]]上播放。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.space.ca/the-expanse-is-coming-to-space/ |title = The Expanse Is Coming To Space, And Here's Why You Should Be Excited |date = 2015-08-27 |publisher = Space |language = en |access-date = 2016-12-17 |archive-date = 2019-07-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190720234434/https://www.space.ca/the-expanse-is-coming-to-space/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>在新西蘭，劇集在{{link-en|Sky電視 (新西蘭)|Sky Television (New Zealand)|Sky}}上播放。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=11598912 |title = The Expanse is the new sci-fi show you're about to binge on |date = 2016-03-03 |publisher = New Zealand Herald |language = en |access-date = 2016-12-17 |archive-date = 2019-12-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191209054628/https://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=11598912 |dead-url = no }}</ref>在所有其他國家，則可在[[Netflix|Netflix]]上播放。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://deadline.com/2016/10/space-drama-the-expanse-streaming-netflix-1201834745/ |title = Space Drama 'The Expanse' Acquired By Netflix For Global Distribution |author = Denise Petski |date = 2016-10-11 |publisher = Deadline Hollywood |language = en |access-date = 2016-12-17 |archive-date = 2021-02-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210204030708/https://deadline.com/2016/10/space-drama-the-expanse-streaming-netflix-1201834745/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

